com.devwebsphere.rediswxs
Interface IRedis<K extends Serializable,V extends Serializable>

All Known Implementing Classes:
RedisMapAdapter
public interface IRedis<K extends Serializable,V extends Serializable>

This provides a data structures API for IBM WebSphere eXtreme Scale. This is modeled after the redis open source project API.

Author:
bnewport
See Also:
R

invokeAsyncOperation

void invokeAsyncOperation(String eventName,
                          Map<String,String> properties)
This invokes an asynchronous event which runs on the server side. It is named and takes parameters. The server side needs to register a handler for that name and then process the event parameters. These are stored in replication memory for fault tolerance, not the database

Parameters:
eventName - The name of the event
properties - The parameters for the event
